  "detailed_description": "<h1>Follow Us</h1><p><strong>We are Herus Games, and most of this game was made by a developer and four students at the time. Welcome to follow us and race together!</strong><br><br>- Twitter: @HorusGames1<br>- Weibo: @HourusGames<br>- QQ group: 126331043<br>- Email: <a href=\"mailto:customer@horusgame.com\">customer@horusgame.com</a>  <br><a href=\"mailto:business@horusgame.com\">business@horusgame.com</a> <br><br>Click and follow our developer home page to be the first to get our updates and new works :)</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Just Ride is a road adventure game. You, retired ace driver Jason, are targeted by an underground organization and need to complete one dangerous mission after another to stay alive ...... But it's not all so frustrating, after all, <strong>the missions aren't always so decent, and neither are the people. </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How strange is it?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Delivering some fries for pocket money before scoping out the evil organization<br>    </li><li>Eavesdropping -- a collection of funny events<br>    </li><li>A rugby ball can be a handy weapon</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693960/extras/bba43dc8866d00c94e9234ae1c93c918.poster.avif?t=1705556719\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693960/extras/bba43dc8866d00c94e9234ae1c93c918.webm?t=1705556719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693960/extras/bba43dc8866d00c94e9234ae1c93c918.mp4?t=1705556719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How exciting is it?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Creating explosive accidents<br>    </li><li>Get out of the explosion trap<br>    </li><li>Explosion! Explosion! MORE exploding!</li></ul><spa